ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[T^{11} 
= \int f(z, \mathbf{p}) E (1-\cos^2 \theta) d^3 \mathbf{p} 
\underbrace{=}_{(4), (6)} J - K \tag{7}\]

<p>ã§ã™ã€‚
åŒæ§˜ã«</p>

\[T^{22} 
= \int f(z, \mathbf{p}) p^2 p^2 c^2 \frac{d^3 \mathbf{p}}{E} 
= J-K \tag{8}\]

<p>ã§ã™ãŒ</p>

\[T_\mu ^{\ \ \mu}
= \int f(z, \mathbf{p}) p_\mu p^\mu c^2 \frac{d^3 \mathbf{p}}{E} 
= 0\]

<p>ã§ãªã‘ã‚Œã°ãªã‚‰ãªã„ãŸã‚ã€\(T^{11}, T^{22}\)ã«ãã‚Œãã‚Œ1/2ã‚’ã‹ã‘ãŸã‚‚ã®ã‚’æœ€çµ‚çš„ãªã‚¨ãƒãƒ«ã‚®ãƒ¼é‹å‹•é‡ãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚½ãƒ«ã¨ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚
ã•ã‚‰ã«</p>

\[T^{01} 
= T^{10}
= \int f(z, \mathbf{p}) E \sin \theta \cos \varphi d^3 \mathbf{p} 
= 0\]

\[T^{12} 
= T^{21} 
= \int f(z, \mathbf{p}) E \sin^2 \theta \cos \varphi \sin \varphi d^3 \mathbf{p} 
= 0\]

<p>ãªã©ã‹ã‚‰ã€å…‰å­ã®ã‚¨ãƒãƒ«ã‚®ãƒ¼é‹å‹•é‡ãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚½ãƒ«ãŒ</p>

\[(T^{\mu \nu}) 
= \left( \begin{array}{cccc}
J &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; H \\
0 &amp; \frac{1}{2} (J-K) &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; \frac{1}{2} (J-K) &amp; 0 \\
